title: Friderichsen (K)
body: Danish botanist who identified the species of the genus Rubus collected by Dr. Vahl in Madeira. Ref.: Rubi fra Madeira (Bot. Tidsskrift, 1905).

Madeira: Location where the species of the genus Rubus were collected
